<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading"><span dir="auto">BSP</span></h1>
 
 
<div id="bodyContent">
 
<div id="siteSub">From linux-sunxi.org</div>
 
 
<div id="contentSub"></div>
 
 
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
Jump to: <a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, <a href="#p-search">search</a>
</div>
 
 
<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>"BSP" means <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Board_support_package"><b>B</b>oard <b>S</b>upport <b>P</b>ackage</a>.
</p><p><br/>
</p>
